What a GOOM!
------------

**********************************
** How to compile on Linux/unix **
**********************************
'./configure'
'make' && 'make install'

** Needed packages **
- xmms-devel
- SDL & SDL-devel


*******************************
** How to compile on MacOS X **
*******************************
In a shell, type the following (without quotes): "./autogen.sh && make"
Do not use "make install"
The iTunes plugin and the standalone app should be built in the mac folder.
Distributor only : The mac Makefile also contains a special "package" target to build the distribution disk image.


